DGE with Seurat

library(Seurat)
library(tidyverse)


filter_DE <- function(df){

  df <- df[df$p_val_adj < 0.05,]

  df["abs_lfc"] <- abs(df$avg_log2FC)

  df <- df[df$abs_lfc > 0.3,]

  df <- df[order(df$avg_log2FC, decreasing = TRUE),] 
  return(df)
}


dat <- readRDS("mm_nk.Rds")
dat = SetIdent(dat, value = "new_label")
